{"tid":2197640,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"想搵返隻舊game(ps1/ps2)","createTime":"2020-09-10T18:33:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T00:18:19.000Z","uid":190472,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"79b1bb4c27b464a9e25295cf561be9bfc66e60f9","tid":2197640,"uid":190472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T18:33:09.000Z","msg":"第一隻應該日本game 黎<br />\n成隻game 好多小遊戲，多數都係用槍射啲目標<br />\n但隻game係偏搞笑但hard core<br />\n例如有一關你得一粒子彈  要射架UFO落黎<br />\n但UFO 係移動得勁快/極難捉到路<br />\n重要限時10秒之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其他小遊戲都係射啲唔同顏色既靶<br />\n我記得係有得雙打，同埋主角個造型都係少少搞笑<br />\n深夜醒起佢有個故事模式  但日文唔知up乜<br />\n依家想睇返<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二隻應該易搵好多  炸彈人白寶<br />\n以前炸彈人係有出過賽車/小遊戲既光碟game<br />\n打機嗰時就係用白寶起城鎮周圍同唔同npc 講野玩小遊戲<br />\n我想搵返有小遊戲合集既白寶<br />\n劇情係一開始起碼頭落船，靠玩小遊戲收集貼紙，就可以開閘去新地區<br />\n又係全部日文當年睇唔明<br />\n<br />\n跪求上面兩隻game 個名，純粹想起youtube 睇返兩隻game同結局講乜<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a3d9492168f1d639c202026c0b3fcf5b0e5ea7a","tid":2197640,"uid":107405,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T18:46:26.000Z","msg":"Bomberman Land 2"},{"pid":"299d5b294949f29e65b7b5d55e3ab896ce38cb8f","tid":2197640,"uid":188922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T18:47:41.000Z","msg":"第一隻拍拍機 機鋪仲有得玩"},{"pid":"7b0b39722198dd502190d62a722e53a844d6232b","tid":2197640,"uid":23535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T18:54:43.000Z","msg":"Gun Bullet<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.biginjap.com/79412-large_default/ps1-gun-bullet.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.biginjap.com%2F79412-large_default%2Fps1-gun-bullet.jpg&h=01ea2d51&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1e97ff19d62e506ba11d59dc363adbc95e7